      <title>美国是菲律宾计划在南海开采石油和天然气的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/us-key-to-philippines-plan-to-tap-oil-gas-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尼拉驻华盛顿特使表示，菲律宾指望美国及其盟国在其在有争议的南中国海勘探能源的计划中发挥关键作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/us-key-to-philippines-plan-to-tap-oil-gas-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
