      <title>拜登警告内塔尼亚胡在斋月开始时不要攻击拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/israel-hamas-deal-elusive-ahead-of-ramadan-as-us-pressure-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登警告以色列不要袭击加沙南部的拉法市，因为与哈马斯的停火谈判在斋月伊始仍陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/israel-hamas-deal-elusive-ahead-of-ramadan-as-us-pressure-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:21:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券投资者正在排队为针对普京的战争提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/bond-investors-are-lining-up-to-fund-the-war-against-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券投资者敦促争论不休的欧盟领导人在国防支出问题上共同采取行动，并使欧盟的万亿欧元债券计划永久化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/bond-investors-are-lining-up-to-fund-the-war-against-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 08:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
